            <p>Boston Nissan 8 5648<lb/></p>
            <p>Revd Dr. S. Morais<lb/>
            My very dear Doctor<lb/></p>
            <p>I just recd. your<lb/> note &#91;&#63;&#93; you<lb/> that we have made<lb/> arrangements &#38; regret<lb/> you could not come<lb/> but hope at some<lb/> future you will be<lb/> here accept our<lb/> most sincere thanks<lb/> for the beautiful<lb/> prayer which you<lb/></p>
            
            <pb n="2"/>
            <p>have so thoughtfully<lb/> prepared&#44; which we<lb/> hope to repay.<lb/></p>
            <p>We understood that<lb/> my children must not<lb/> visit the Burial ground<lb/> during the month of<lb/> Nissan<lb/></p>
            <p>If you are not engaged<lb/> tomorrow could you<lb/> be at the Telephone Comp<lb/> office at 4. P. M<lb/></p>
            <p><sic>Your&#39;s</sic> very sincerely<lb/>
            Alfred A Marcus<lb/></p>
        </body>
